and Budget Management Act, 2003.

239
00:10:47,894 --> 00:10:49,110
According to this Act,

240
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:50,954
the government's target should be

241
00:10:50,954 --> 00:10:54,870
to keep the fiscal deficit at only 3% of nominal GDP.

242
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:58,295
But since then, there has been only one year,

243
00:10:58,295 --> 00:11:00,401
around 2007-08,

244
